UID:TR0-9NOl2xgmv2ZagvNJr
SUMMARY:City of Renton 2026 State of the City with Mayor Armondo Pavone
DTSTAMP:20260322T022258Z
DTSTART:20260326T003000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join Mayor Armondo Pavone during his annual State of the City o
	n Wednesday\, March 25\, at 6:30 p.m. at Hyatt Regency. Come hear directly
	 from Mayor Pavone on 2025 accomplishments\, future plans\, and how the ci
	ty is addressing challenges.  5:30 p.m. - Reception 6:30 p.m. - Presentati
