SUMMARY:North End Ecosocialism Reading Group
DTSTAMP:20260322T022258Z
DTSTART:20260326T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us at Armistice Coffee Roosevelt\\\, to discuss the book P
	ractical Radicals: Seven Strategies to Change the World\\\, by Deepak Bhar
	gava and Stephanie Luce\\\, through the end of Chapter 11. \\nYou don’t ha
	ve to live in the north end\\\, and you can feel free to join the conversa
