DESCRIPTION:General Admission Only Tours depart promptly at their scheduled
	 time. Please arrive early to facilitate security screening. If you arrive
	 late\, there are no guarantees tour guides will wait for you or your part
	y. Tour guests will enter doors inside the Pro-Shop off Occidental Ave. Si
	gns will direct you to the appropriate door. There is no extended field ac
